{"tid":1345701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣］元朗恐襲","createTime":"2019-07-22T02:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:51:26.000Z","uid":111316,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a92ebbfbd9c729b811f9aeda8a9a4842e9c20356","tid":1345701,"uid":111316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再講政治嘅嘢唔關自己事<br />\n而家黑社會打人 警察放行<br />\n如果唔係政府容許呢d事情<br />\n根本無可能離譜到咁<br />\n<br />\n今日訓係地下的係一個大肚婆<br />\n難保他日 可能仲包括你身邊熟悉的人<br />\n佢未必要係黃絲 佢最初未必唔支持警察<br />\n但佢果日出現係唔岩的時間地點<br />\n佢就有機會比人打<br />\n<br />\n如果你仲好意思反問好人好者會係果個時間地點出現咩咩咩<br />\n睇清楚啦！港鐵站黎！出街食完飯番屋企嘅時間黎！<br />\n<br />\n呢個政府已經無意政治事情政治了結<br />\n班高官係唔係仲值得你地去擁護支持？<br />\n示威者的暴力 劍指政權<br />\n政警鄉黑暴力 手刃平民<br />\n<br />\n警察可以擘大眼講大話<br />\n話班元朗叔父無武器係手唔拉得<br />\n但係見到著黑衫的市民行過<br />\n就查身分證 遊街示眾 放支水都話你可能襲警<br />\n呢一班公僕 係服務市民 定係服務政權鄉親？<br />\n真係除暴安良 定係喪盡天良？<br />\n<br />\n附上早幾日已在網上流傳<br />\n《一班AO的分享》<br />\n當中的劇本已經一一出現<br />\n當權者掩耳盜鈴<br />\n作為香港人的你<br />\n係唔係仲要選擇沉默是金？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2336638383089638?s=1407176977&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F178965725523592%2Fposts%2F2336638383089638%3Fs%3D1407176977%26sfns%3Dmo&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=36f9671a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2336638383089638?s=1407176977&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70248bee9d607fa9bd419c663945c1b9e0333e1f","tid":1345701,"uid":53515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:40:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗係發生恐襲呀屌你老母</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6d04a40af296c61b9bc5fc9d9806efa71e4c5a0d","tid":1345701,"uid":53515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:40:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗係發生恐襲呀屌你老母</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ebb27f4dd0eaf7b8e7ce59c52843393daace7a07","tid":1345701,"uid":54125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>上環係暴力鎮壓，元朗係恐怖襲擊</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"73719f88c0e1108c56872ee6122368dd5c922155","tid":1345701,"uid":111316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:42:51.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"eebe3da11e497173eb7ecd795512e510b4039905","tid":1345701,"uid":38666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:44:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請定性為恐怖襲擊</span></span>"},{"pid":"037763d1eb4ca641484bc18ce445378655f20327","tid":1345701,"uid":279095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"香港政府勾結黑社會"},{"pid":"755bdcc6952cf3fb5d85a8ee6c9a401bcd7ad5db","tid":1345701,"uid":111316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:50:00.000Z","msg":"我真係好想問班中間派<br />\n官商鄉黑做曬係你地面前<br />\n仲話唔需要調查委員會？"},{"pid":"33bd89096c77d1523ee38709c1f944b5c94190ee","tid":1345701,"uid":271199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:50:35.000Z","msg":"721元朗事件定性 &quot; 恐怖襲擊 &quot;，元朗圍村佬列為 &quot; 恐怖分子 &quot;，達成共識，文宣行動，要全部人知道。"},{"pid":"9c37fdec0b711cf37823bbd7b2bb8194b3bde404","tid":1345701,"uid":271199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:50:46.000Z","msg":"721元朗事件定性 &quot; 恐怖襲擊 &quot;，元朗圍村佬列為 &quot; 恐怖分子 &quot;，達成共識，文宣行動，要全部人知道。"},{"pid":"0edee5e9375f7a6f71dbe3b543bb9e1a4ac88aac","tid":1345701,"uid":271199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:51:00.000Z","msg":"721元朗事件定性 &quot; 恐怖襲擊 &quot;，元朗圍村佬列為 &quot; 恐怖分子 &quot;，達成共識，文宣行動，要全部人知道。"},{"pid":"cc9899c4ab4bd4331ed88d68f9f07c